Type: Package
Package: teal.picks
Title: Dataset and Variable Picker and Merge Module for 'teal' Applications
Version: 0.1.0.9233
Date: 2026-04-30
Authors@R:
    person("insightsengineering", , , "insightsengineering@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Allows users to interactively select datasets, variables, and values
    within 'teal' applications using a 'tidyselect'-style interface. Selected
    picks can be merged and transformed into analysis-ready data within 'teal'
    modules.
License: Apache License 2.0
